org.hkijena.acaq5.api.algorithm

Class ACAQAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.acaq5.api.algorithm.ACAQAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ACAQValidatable, ACAQParameterHolder
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ACAQCompartmentOutput, ACAQFileDataSource, ACAQFileListDataSource, ACAQFolderDataSource, ACAQFolderListDataSource, ACAQIteratingAlgorithm, ACAQProjectCompartment, ACAQTraitNode, AnnotateAll, GraphWrapperAlgorithm, ImageTypeConverter, MergeDataEnhancer, RemoveAnnotations, SplitByAnnotation

    public abstract class ACAQAlgorithm
extends Object
implements ACAQValidatable, ACAQParameterHolder
    An algorithm is is a set of input and output data slots, and a run() function It is part of the ACAQAlgorithmGraph
